There have been a lot of frustrations about the fact that it lasted so little and the most important is the fact that we are still very friends with Bruce (Fairweather) and Greg (Gilmore) who started in the band with us and when I listen to a song or I see a photo I think about the incredible person Andy was and how he made me laugh, it has always been a pleasure to work, laugh, talk about music, football and many other things with him.
